aa(lp346
VAnd yet we still insist, by and large,
p347
aVin thinking that we can understand China
p348
aVby simply drawing on Western experience,
p349
aVlooking at it through Western eyes,
p350
aVusing Western concepts.
p351
aVIf you want to know why
p352
aVwe unerringly seem to get China wrong \u2014
p353
