p354
aVthis is the reason.
p355
aVUnfortunately, I think,
p356
aVI have to say that I think
p357
aVattitude towards China
p358
aVis that of a kind of little Westerner mentality.
p359
aVIt's kind of arrogant.
p360
aVIt's arrogant in the sense
p361
aVthat we think that we are best,
p362
aVand therefore we have the universal measure.
p363
